Description: Hermes agent as primary desktop environment for DuckBotOS
 Installs Hermes (NousResearch hermes-agent) as the primary AI agent
 and desktop surface for DuckBotOS.
 .
 Hermes provides:
 - Web Dashboard at http://localhost:9119 (chat, sessions, TUI)
 - Gateway API at http://localhost:9110 (for MCP and tool integration)
 - CLI: hermes gateway start / hermes chat / hermes tools
 - Skills system, memory, cron, messaging gateway
 - Sub-agent spawning, multi-agent coordination
 - Voice features: wake-word detection, speech-to-text, text-to-speech
 .
 In DuckBotOS, Hermes runs as a systemd user service and the Weston
 kiosk loads the web dashboard in fullscreen Chromium.
 .
 Homepage: https://github.com/nousresearch/hermes-agent
Version: 0.17 (Reach)